199
00:16:12,797 --> 00:16:14,799
Parang pagbating istilong kanluranin.

200
00:16:15,341 --> 00:16:16,384
Dapat mong malaman

201
00:16:16,468 --> 00:16:18,511
Ganito ang
pagbati ng mga tao sa ibang bansa.

202
00:16:18,595 --> 00:16:20,305
